{"tid":1287280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗某電話維修店被警察恐嚇","createTime":"2019-07-05T06:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T15:14:43.000Z","uid":99610,"like":1063,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":122,"replies":[{"pid":"65980de97600f8f0712254e0581720ba2524e856","tid":1287280,"uid":99610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"<code>（強烈譴責聲明）\n由於香港警察恐嚇我屋企人，並在香港不斷製造白色恐怖\n以致這幾天公司未能運作正常，店東深感抱歉\n\n鑒於7月4號凌晨，我全家屋企人受到香港警察滋擾\n恐嚇老人家，恐嚇大肚婆，並搶大肚婆手機，嚇小朋友，全屋人親眼見證呢件事發生\n\n並在搜查期間，不斷作出威嚇，如果不乖乖認，不順從他們旨意，他們說就會去我鋪頭取走所有客人的手機，以作威脅\n\n期間細細聲講：「如果你唔合作，我就去你鋪頭拎晒你客人D電話走，唔知一扣一查要扣幾年」\n\n行為極其卑劣\n\n恐嚇期間，當時屋企沒有電腦，以及身穿無袋短褲\n所以當時屈唔到「藏有兒童色情物品」/「藏毒」等問題\n\n 如果有記者朋友想問可以再講，以上句句全部屬實\n\n同如果暫時想整電話，可以inbox問\n原先電話號碼/whatsapp有問題，會暫時打唔通</code><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/545772952127123/posts/2207983129239422?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F545772952127123%2Fposts%2F2207983129239422%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=9c9b386d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/545772952127123/posts/2207983129239422?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c58ad77f8a671980e3a25c7efd248fd11d9e1f","tid":1287280,"uid":61520,"like":159,"dislike":1,"score":158,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:46:15.000Z","msg":"唔想再係咁。。。<br />\n<br />\n幫手俾意見<br />\n<br />\n一人一信  no DQ  還我選舉權  <br />\n唔好比藉口人地將好的議員篩走<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F271467.typeform.com%2Fto%2FMTUjKV&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h