uto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/579355445500005/posts/1893016190800584?s=588337283&amp;sfns=xmwa</a><br />\n<br />\n中學生發起罷課：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199644</a><br />\n<br />\n新假期野餐攻略：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.weekendhk.com/&hellip;/weekend-leisure/野餐-添馬公園-香港好去處/2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fweekend-leisure%2F%E9%87%8E%E9%A4%90-%E6%B7%BB%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%BD%E5%8E%BB%E8%99%95%2F2%2F&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BDsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=90983c20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.weekendhk.com/&hellip;/weekend-leisure/野餐-添馬公園-香港好去處/2/</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n［好撚重要，廣傳］多圖抗爭手冊（裝備list）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1197512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1197512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ebb36b595f4584e71aefcdd5d64cce945c829ef6","tid":1287280,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察 知法犯法</span></span>"},{"pid":"d357586ab47c922f3fa0f0e682b5863091c1816f","tid":1287280,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feec60775973564b4cf2dd93cf211d558c78b550","tid":1287280,"uid":174566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffbecf204956882b5e9c2778fb48f5360e796ed","tid":12